wiki.summary: On “F.N,” emerging rapper Lil Tjay speaks about his friend snitching on him after getting caught partaking in gang activities. The eponymous track shows Tjay reflecting on his difficult upbringing and come up, while also boasting about the lavish lifestyle he now lives. In the week ending October 26, 2019, the track peaked at #56 on the Billboard Hot 100. On January 25, 2021, “F.N“ was certified 3x platinum by the RIAA. Read more on Last.fm.
